{"tid":101533,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"JR由東京去名古屋，上網無得訂？","createTime":"2017-01-31T02:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T07:12:05.000Z","uid":25652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe2bd59afcc1ab302f27bc025a31c6d50de459b9","tid":101533,"uid":25652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:26:14.000Z","msg":"我搵後搵去都係得JR East有網上訂票系統，但揀東海道新幹線又無得揀Nagoya...<br />\n<br />\n請問巴絲打，買跨區JR飛係要walk-in 當地買？我打算之後由東京去名古屋，然後由名古屋去大阪"},{"pid":"9eda0c95883b7ac76e86b4de91d6a940c9259466","tid":101533,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:37:41.000Z","msg":"ekinet有得訂東海道新幹線喎，我訂去京都既飛都係咁拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29818cd735f9bf88060dedfddf56bea6fd224a1","tid":101533,"uid":49344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:08:48.000Z","msg":"試下 jr 東海"},{"pid":"df9b0ee90facc25095eed0de23a5f33a1e02149e","tid":101533,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"JR East日文版eki-net先可以訂東海道新幹線<br />\n中文同英文版都訂唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n東海道新幹線喺JR Central(JR東海)嘅路線<br />\n佢個訂票系統要會員先用得，兼且要有日本信用卡同住址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果唔係繁忙日子，去到車站買即班仲方便<br />\n反正班次仲密過香港機場快線/澳門噴射船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0eedbbb6eab289b6341758ad9151ac4eb024519","tid":101533,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5212cd5744a1fa2b1261804e91826eb7554db312","tid":101533,"uid":25652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:02:01.000Z","msg":"唔該各位！<br />\n咁睇黎我應該會直接walk-in買，見網上嘅都係買JR Pass,  但我只係單程由東京去名古屋，再由名古屋去大阪，買Pass好似無乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dc7eda5cbdfd2dabf02b39cfd54fcdda21a88a","tid":101533,"uid":7796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"坐巴士啦<br />\nWiller express"},{"pid":"8131ff0b39de85dfd8da5e7c3fc5e80cb3b20042","tid":101533,"uid":25652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐巴士啦<br />\nWiller express</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東京去名古屋要5粒幾鐘喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我怕坐到屎忽痛。<br />\n不過都係一種方法，如果我walk-in買唔到JR，我會用呢個方法。感謝！"},{"pid":"85d995398b8c1edbab6bc23c588c4a5893c0f48e","tid":101533,"uid":61497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>坐巴士啦<br />\nWiller express</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東京去名古屋要5粒幾鐘喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我怕坐到屎忽痛。<br />\n不過都係一種方法，如果我walk-in買唔到JR，我會用呢個方法。感謝！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇可能冇位，記得買のぞみ ，最快"},{"pid":"018786118e7a76cb51bb101bbf7876cf3252f996","tid":101533,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>坐巴士啦<br />\nWiller express</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東京去名古屋要5粒幾鐘喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我怕坐到屎忽痛。<br />\n不過都係一種方法，如果我walk-in買唔到JR，我會用呢個方法。感謝！</blockquote><br />\n無可能買唔到新幹線飛，Nozomi+Hikari+Kodama加埋同地鐵差唔多密<br />\n同埋佢下下16輛編成好難無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51b8e25f7c6a37244f9404b13ea298be80985a6","tid":101533,"uid":25652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>坐巴士啦<br />\nWiller express</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東京去名古屋要5粒幾鐘喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我怕坐到屎忽痛。<br />\n不過都係一種方法，如果我walk-in買唔到JR，我會用呢個方法。感謝！</blockquote><br />\n無可能買唔到新幹線飛，Nozomi+Hikari+Kodama加埋同地鐵差唔多密<br />\n同埋佢下下16輛編成好難無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝！咁我就放心了。<br />\nBtw, 想問下由名古屋去大阪個程係唔係要到左名古屋先買到？我係東京應該買唔到？"},{"pid":"8d3459129507b7b950ef4fc71f74659d55d40311","tid":101533,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>坐巴士啦<br />\nWiller express</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東京去名古屋要5粒幾鐘喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我怕坐到屎忽痛。<br />\n不過都係一種方法，如果我walk-in買唔到JR，我會用呢個方法。感謝！</blockquote><br />\n無可能買唔到新幹線飛，Nozomi+Hikari+Kodama加埋同地鐵差唔多密<br />\n同埋佢下下16輛編成好難無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n感謝！咁我就放心了。<br />\nBtw, 想問下由名古屋去大阪個程係唔係要到左名古屋先買到？我係東京應該買唔到？</blockquote><br />\n東京買埋都得<br />\n講清楚班次就okay"},{"pid":"cd046291cdb1081add10501ab1d87619ad99eee7","tid":101533,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff5c398cf7cb994779a79607cd666bf342e1cfd5","tid":101533,"uid":29075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"坐中央本線去啦"},{"pid":"cd869e3c8d872043a17eee99d7716c208a1fbaa4","tid":101533,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐中央本線去啦</blockquote><br />\n東海道本線重好喇"},{"pid":"4f8f58fb08ba9ec9ec1dcae7e8cdbaec67078598","tid":101533,"uid":65939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:59:20.000Z","msg":"試下夜行巴士,慳返晚酒店又訓得舒覺<br />\n<br />\n上年10月先試過一次,用最平價果架車都覺得訓得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e115c41ba7b3fce6893c9a2d82d1fe0f48b65ee3","tid":101533,"uid":49344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>坐中央本線去啦</blockquote><br />\n東海道本線重好喇</blockquote><br />\n不如坐中央新幹線啦"},{"pid":"b8939c4715e38d8e1a8072333b30ca4987a98e45","tid":101533,"uid":19949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T07:12:0